name: Pink Coversations
description:
Glitch edit of a video-collage made from other glitch edits deemed by myself as "not good enough" during selection process. Re-worked in an attempt to give the essence of this pieces a chance to be shared when they werent meant to. Perhaps also a silly way for me to be or feel inclusive with all the parts of my process and stop disregarding pieces that also make me feel an emotional impulse and are part of a "final" creation.
 
                             And here they are, having a conversation, in pink.
